    (def addr-1    (Address. &quot;123 Main St&quot; &quot;Anytown&quot;))
    (def person-1  (Person.  &quot;Joe Smith&quot; addr-1))
    
    (someClass-&gt;clj  person-1)    ; Convert Java person-1 obj

You will get a Clojure map back that looks like:

    {:name      &quot;Joe Smith&quot;
